Package sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.soql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callable
    This interface is used to represent "function" valued properties in ScriptObjects.
    JSJavaFactory  
    ObjectVisitor
    This visitor is supplied to SOQLEngine.executeQuery to receive result set objects one by one.
    ScriptObject
    Any Java object supporting this interface can be accessed from scripts with "simpler" access pattern.
